      "author_association" : "MEMBER",
      "body" : "I was wrong: the 05fa54d56b8ed61925c0a7b58d505130162263df commit is misleading. There is nothing macOS specific in SC1087, SC2206, SC2207, SC2230 and SC2236 warnings.\r\nThe point is the default `shellcheck` version on bionic is:\r\n```\r\n$ /usr/bin/shellcheck -V | grep version:\r\nversion: 0.4.6\r\n```\r\n\r\nBut we use version `0.6.0` (see #15166).\r\n\r\nThe misleading commit will be removed today.",
